>\n救護人員抵達現場後立即為傷者進行治理，並於凌晨1時41分將傷者送往伊利沙伯醫院急症室。在整個救援行動中，本處救護人員並沒有受到警方或其他人士的阻撓。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警甴有阻救護車前科<br />\n星期六消防處又話聯同警隊止暴制亂<br />\n誠信破產，唔會有人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:20:03.000Z","msg":"留意送往 =\\= 送到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:21:14.000Z","msg":"送往係41分 真係有30分鐘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:30:39.000Z","msg":"咪就係我想講嘅嘢，可能到醫院已經係成個鐘"},{"pid":"9968dc396cfe5be971148013ca538315435d0f9d","tid":1694561,"uid":11354,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e85663b6acfe6a7ab1e5bdd4d3a10962448b095c","tid":1694561,"uid":251414,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:28:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20190913/s00001/1568313573342/消防-警兩稱太子站無傷者擋救護-19救護入站共花1小時-「救援角度上唔係咁好」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190913%2Fs00001%2F1568313573342%2F%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2-%E8%AD%A6%E5%85%A9%E7%A8%B1%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E7%84%A1%E5%82%B7%E8%80%85%E6%93%8B%E6%95%91%E8%AD%B7-19%E6%95%91%E8%AD%B7%E5%85%A5%E7%AB%99%E5%85%B1%E8%8A%B11%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82-%E3%80%8C%E6%95%91%E6%8F%B4%E8%A7%92%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8A%E5%94%94%E4%BF%82%E5%92%81%E5%A5%BD%E3%80%8D&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwGo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=55772260\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190913%2Fs00001%2F1568313573342%2F%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2-%E8%AD%A6%E5%85%A9%E7%A8%B1%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E7%84%A1%E5%82%B7%E8%80%85%E6%93%8B%E6%95%91%E8%AD%B7-19%E6%95%91%E8%AD%B7%E5%85%A5%E7%AB%99%E5%85%B1%E8%8A%B11%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82-%E3%80%8C%E6%95%91%E6%8F%B4%E8%A7%92%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8A%E5%94%94%E4%BF%82%E5%92%81%E5%A5%BD%E3%80%8D&h=297bba07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20190913/